description.en: Ubiq is a decentralized platform which allows the creation and implementation of smart contracts and decentralized applications. Built upon an improved Ethereum codebase, the Ubiq blockchain acts as a large globally distributed ledger and supercomputer, allowing developers to create decentralized and automated solutions to thousands of tasks which today are carried out by third party intermediaries.

status_updates.description:
Ubiq has today been listed on two new exchanges, with markets for the Korean/Canadian based 'Dove Wallet' and Chinese based 'BitZ' now available for trading.

The primary market for both is based in UBQ/USDT, however, Dove Wallet has a large number of secondary markets, including KRW, GBP, ETH, BTC and more.

https://dovewallet.com/en/trade/spot/ubq-usdt
https://www.bitz.cm/exchange/ubq_usdt

$UBQ #Ubiq

This weekend Ubiq successfully performed a hard fork network upgrade with our Taurus release, as of block 1,500,000.

This update activated Istanbul EIP’s from upstream Ethereum.

For more details on the upgrade you can watch this short video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WVrKYCY7jiM

$UBQ #Ubiq

Earlier today, Bittrex US and Global exchanges launched a USDT market for Ubiq in addition to our already existing BTC market.

The Ubiq team would like to thank Bittrex for their continued support. The community can trade UBQ for USDT here:

https://bittrex.com/Market/Index?MarketName=USDT-UBQ

$UBQ

Ubiq is proud to present 'POSTER 0 — SHINOBI', the first NFT to launch on the Ubiq platform and created by community member Tunachum.

The response to the first Ubiq NFT was overwhelming, with it completely selling out in 34 minutes!

We will be launching more NFT's in the near future, so stay tuned for more announcements.

https://blog.ubiqsmart.com/ubiq-launches-its-first-redeemable-nft-39e70bf1084

Ubiq is proud to announce that the first Yield farm (a form of staking) has been launched. This farm serves 2 purposes which is to introduce the community to Yield farming and to set up the concept of the Ubiq Token Generation Event Framework.

Read more here: https://blog.ubiqsmart.com/launch-of-the-ubiq-token-generation-event-framework-842bd50274cd

Ubiq would like to announce the Taurus hard fork, which is planned to activate at block 1,500,000, currently estimated for March 20, 2021.

This update will activate Istanbul EIP’s from upstream Ethereum.

The article below outlines the changes and is recommended reading:

https://blog.ubiqsmart.com/announcing-the-taurus-hard-fork-and-gubiq-5-0-3184c5564fcf

$UBQ

We are proud to announce the launch of Shinobi for the Ubiq community.

Shinobi is a decentralized protocol for automated liquidity provision on Ubiq, built on a Uniswap V2 codebase.

We recommend our community read our guides on: https://ubiq.ninja/dojo

You can reach Shinobi by visiting: https://shinobi.ubiq.ninja/

#defi #UBQ
